```plantuml
@startuml eqbal_CarND_Capstone_CarX

package "Self-Driving Car System" {
    [Traffic Light Detection Node] as TLNode
    [Camera Info Publisher] as CameraNode
    [Waypoint Loader] as WPLoader
    [Waypoint Updater] as WPUpdater
    [Waypoint Follower] as WPFollower
    [Twist Controller (DBW)] as DBWNode
    [PID Controller] as PID
    [Yaw Controller] as Yaw
    [LowPass Filter] as LPF
    [Bridge Node] as Bridge
}

node "Simulator" as Simulator
node "Real Car (CARLA)" as Carla

TLNode --> CameraNode : uses calibration
TLNode --> WPUpdater : traffic light status
WPLoader --> WPUpdater : waypoint data
WPUpdater --> WPFollower : adjusted waypoints
WPFollower --> DBWNode : target velocities
DBWNode --> PID : throttle control
DBWNode --> Yaw : steering control
DBWNode --> LPF : signal filtering
Bridge --> Simulator : connects
Bridge --> Carla : connects

note top of DBWNode: Implements actuator control\nfor steering, throttle, brake
note right of WPFollower: Uses Pure Pursuit algorithm\nfor path following
note left of WPUpdater: Adjusts waypoints based on\ntraffic lights & obstacles

@enduml
```